Limbo P1 - Salek's Last LT

General info

Additional Info
Paragon level run detected.

Since I don't have any KV data at all I had to make a few guesses regarding the mobs faced.

The new paragon areas introduced new damage types.
HGX neither detects nor counts these damage types. For this report I have mapped them by hand to the damage type INTERNAL otherwise they would have not been included.

The new damage types of particular interest for this report are: (BLIGHT), DECEPTION, DEGENERATION and DIGESTION
